HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!!! Beautiful curb appeal!! This property offers 2 Bedrooms 1.75 bathrooms 2157 SF of oversized living room and dining rooms with neutral tile floor throughout. Featuring an abundance of natural lighting which is perfect for Relaxing and Entertaining. Gourmet eat in Kitchen vaulted ceiling with huge Center Island and  bay window and Breakfast Nook and built in cabinetry. Retreat to your Massive owners suite with updated walk-in shower and also a large second bedroom. Laundry room area big enough for an office/hobby room. Private  backyard with an enclosed AZ room and BBQ area with pavered patio to enjoy AZ Evenings. Solar Lease!! LOW LOW Monthly Utility Bills!
